'''砷化钠'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，由[[钠|钠]]和[[砷|砷]]两种元素组成，化学式为Na<sub>3</sub>As。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.americanelements.com/sodium-arsenide-12044-25-6|title=Sodium Arsenide|last=Elements|first=American|website=American Elements|access-date=2018-12-05|archive-date=2019-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328095537/https://www.americanelements.com/sodium-arsenide-12044-25-6|dead-url=no}}</ref>它可由砷和钠在200–400 °C的化合反应得到，遇水或空气分解。<ref>{{Cite book | author = E. Dönges | title = Alkali Metals | work = Handbook of Preparative Inorganic Chemistry | edition = 2nd | editor = G. Brauer | publisher = Academic Press | date = 1963 | location = New York | page = 986 }}</ref> 

它和镧系元素氯化物（LnCl<sub>3</sub>，Ln=Pr, Nd, Sm, Gd, Tb, Dy, Er, Yb）在700~800 °C发生复分解反应，得到相应的砷化物LnAs。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Materials Chemistry|volume=4|issue=2|language=en|issn=0959-9428|date=1994|pages=285|doi=10.1039/jm9940400285|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=jm9940400285|title=Metathesis routes to lanthanide pnictides|accessdate=2021-01-20|author=Jonathan C. Fitzmaurice, Ivan P. Parkin, Adrian T. Rowley}}</ref>它在液氨中和过渡金属氯化物反应，也能得到相应的[[砷化物|砷化物]]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=40|issue=27|language=en|issn=0020-1669|date=2001-12|pages=6940–6947|doi=10.1021/ic010648s|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ic010648s|title=Liquid Ammonia Mediated Metathesis: Synthesis of Binary Metal Chalcogenides and Pnictides|accessdate=2021-01-20|author=G. A. Shaw, I. P. Parkin}}</ref>它和[[砷化铕|砷化铕]]在800 °C反应，可以得到Na<sub>2</sub>Eu<sub>3</sub>As<sub>4</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Solid State Chemistry|volume=97|issue=1|language=en|date=1992-03|pages=1–9|doi=10.1016/0022-4596(92)90002-D|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/002245969290002D|title=On the structure and some properties of novel ternary pnictides: Na2M3Y4 (M = Sr, Eu; Y = P, As)|accessdate=2021-01-20|author=Wolfgang Hönle, Jianhua Lin, Martin Hartweg, Hans-Georg von Schnering|archive-date=2018-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702031202/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/002245969290002D|dead-url=no}}</ref>
